title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 7 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 7 2022
description:
A clear self-defense case in New York City. Fury at woke Manhattan DA Alvin Bragg for prosecuting hardworking bodega employee, 62, who stabbed career criminal to death in self-defense. GoFundMe REMOVES the man’s $20k legal fund as he languishes in Rikers on $250,000 bond. Newly released video of suspect shooting at police in Akron, Ohio. Joining Clay and Buck, Bryan Dean Wright, former CIA ops officer and host of The President’s Daily Brief podcast on iHeart. Wright discusses the rise of China, why everyone should uninstall TikTok and Biden's many foreign policy failures.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
